Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.99,0:00:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0BD7D5&\i0\fn华文行楷\fs24\pos(516,336)}翻译  校对：幸福ing形式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉到阳光拂面\NI feel the sun on my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了绿树环身\NI see trees all around me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,野花在微风中吐露芬芳\Nscent of wildflowers on a breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如此怡人\NIt's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在这一刻  我并不是身陷太空\NIn this moment, I'm not stranded in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,距地球上的人类遭核难灭顶事件\NIt's been 97 years since a nuclear apocalypse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,已经97年了\Nkilled everyone on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只留下辐射在那个星球暗流涌动\Nleaving the planet simmering in radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,幸运的是  还有幸存者\NFortunately, there were survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在爆炸发生那一刻\N12 nations had operational space stations
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,12个国家运行着太空站\Nat the time of the bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如今只剩方舟号了\NThere is now only The Ark,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,由众多太空站锻造而成\None station forged from the many.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被告知地球还需100年\NWe're told the Earth needs another 100 years
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,才能适宜人类居住\Nto become survivable again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:00:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,困于太空四代之久\N4 more space-locked generations,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,人类才能回家  回到地球\Nand man can go home, back to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,地球  梦之所向  这就是事实\NThe ground, that's the dream. This is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,319号囚徒  面朝墙\NPrisoner 319, face the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,现实烂透了\NReality sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这是干嘛？\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,安静  伸出右臂\NQuiet. Hold out your right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是  我时候还没到\NNo. No. It's not my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再有一个月我才18\NI don't turn 18 for another month.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出你右臂\NHold out your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在方舟号上  任何罪名\NOn The Ark, every crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,无论大小  均被判以死刑\Nno matter how small, is punishable by death
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 除非你未满18岁  - 你的表\N- unless you're under 18. - Your watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.55,0:01:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不  这是我爸爸的\NNo. It was my father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 取下来  - 不\N- Take it off. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,少年犯均被关在此处…看管\NJuvenile offenders get put here... lockup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们叫它天箱\NWe call it the sky box.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,319号囚徒\NPrisoner 319...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarke  站住  在这儿等着\NClarke, stop. Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈？妈妈  发生什么了？\NMom? Mom, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么回事儿？\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  走\NCome on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要杀了我们  是吗\NThey're killing us all, aren't they,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要为剩下的人活着\Nreducing population to make more time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,缩减人口吗？\Nfor the rest of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarke  你不是在被处决\NClarke, you are not being executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你要被送往地球\NYou're being sent to the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们100个人\Nall 100 of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？但这并不安全\NWhat? But it's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不不\NNo. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们18岁时会被复审\NWe get reviewed at 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,条律变更了\NThe rules have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这给了你活下来的机会\NThis gives you a chance to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你会优先照料他人\NYour instincts will tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的本能使然\Nto take care of everybody else first,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如同你的父亲  但是一切小心\Njust like your father, but be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能连你也失去\NI can't lose you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我太爱你了\NI love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,地球  Clarke\NEarth, Clarke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去地球了\NYou get to go to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0BD7D5&\i0\fn华文行楷\fs28\pos(358,338)}地球百子 第一季第一集\N—— 真 爱 字 幕 组 ——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来\NWelcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wells  你为什么在这儿？\NWells, why the hell are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,当我发现他们在送囚犯\NWhen I found out they were sending prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,去地球  我就故意被他们抓了\Nto the ground, I got myself arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,为你而来\NI came for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是大气层\NThat was the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,方舟号的囚徒们  听好了\NPrisoners of The Ark, here me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们被给予再次机会\NYou've been given a second chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,身为你们的长官\Nand as your Chancellor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你们明白\Nit is my hope that you see this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这个机会不仅是你们的\Nas not just a chance for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我们的\Nbut a chance for all of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是人类众生的\Nindeed for mankind itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对你们降落地境遇一无所知\NWe have no idea what is waiting for you down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如果幸存率较高\NIf the odds of survival were better,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会派送其他人\Nwe would've sent others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白说  之所以送你们去\NFrankly, we're sending you because
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为犯罪使你们毫无价值\Nyour crimes have made you expendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wells  你爸真混蛋\NYour dad is a dick, Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的罪行会被赦免\NThose crimes will be forgiven,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,记录会被清除\Nyour records wiped clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,20分钟前我看到一架飞船被发射\NI saw a ship launch not more than 20 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在里边？\NWho was on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是囚禁者吗？他们还只是孩子\NWas it the prisoners? They're just kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是去地球了吗？\NAre they going to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么变动吗？\NHas something changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,各位  如我所说  此时\NFolks, as I said, at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们无法证实或否认任何事\Nwe cannot confirm or deny anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  女士\NCome on, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子在那架飞船上\NMy son is on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,降落点经过精挑细选\NThe drop site has been chosen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,最后次大战前  韦瑟山\NBefore the last war, Mount Weather
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,曾是建于高山里的军事基地\Nwas a military base built within a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,库存了足量的不易腐坏物资\NIt was to be stocked with enough non-perishables
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可供300人两年使用\Nto sustain 300 people for up to two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太空漫步强势回归\NSpacewalk bandit strikes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,继续啊  Finn！\NGo, Finn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧\NCheck it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你老爸最终还是让我漂浮了\NYour dad floated me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,迫降伞打开前你应该坐好了\NYou should strap in before the parachutes deploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你俩  想活命就别解开\NHey, you two, stay put if you want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,韦瑟山就是生命之源\NMount Weather is life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须马上找到这些物资\NYou must locate those supplies immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是那个\Nyou're the traitor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,被监禁一年的背叛者？\Nwho's been in solitary for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,而你就是那个因为非法太空漫步\NYou're the idiot who wasted a month of oxygen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而浪费一个月氧气的白痴\Non an illegal spacewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但那很有趣\NBut it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫Finn\NI'm Finn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的职责之一是活下去\NYour one responsibility is stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,呆你座位上\NStay in your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Finn  你还好吗？\NFinn, are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,先别说\NNot now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看到的就是\NTotal system failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,系统完全失效\Nthat's what we're looking at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所知道的是当我们失去联系\NAll we know for sure is that they were off course
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他们偏离了航道  所以…\Nwhen we lost contact, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那通讯网络呢\NTell me about communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,除了他们手腕上的遥感装置\NOther than the telemetry from their wristbands,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,其他一无所获…没有音频  没有视频\Nwe got nothing... no audio, no video,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也没电脑链接\Nno computer link.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所有为协助他们而植入的程序\NEverything that we programmed in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,都失效了\Nto help them is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只能靠自己了\NThey're on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,推进器现在也该打开了\NRetrorockets ought to have fired by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这飞船上的所有东西\NOk. Everything on this ship
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,都有百年寿命了吧\Nis 100 years old, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,让飞船飞一会儿\NJust give it a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarke  我必须得告诉你\NClarke, there's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉害你父亲被捕\NI'm sorry I got your father arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你别和我谈我父亲\NDon't you talk about my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  我不能在临死前\NPlease, I can't die knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还让你恨我\Nthat you hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有逮捕我父亲  Wells\NThey didn't arrest my father, Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们处决了他  我也恨实了你\NThey executed him. I do hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,听\NListen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没机器的轰鸣声了\NNo machine hum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哇噢\NWhoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还是头一次\NThat's a first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Finn  他还有呼吸吗？\NFinn, is he breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,外舱门气压变低了\NThe outer door is on the lower level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们走吧  - 不\N- Let's go. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能就这样开门\NWe can't just open the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  就推上闸就行了  伙计们\NHey, just back it up, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,别打开\NStop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,空气可能有毒\NThe air could be toxic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何  我们都是死\NIf the air is toxic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就算空气有毒\Nwe're all dead, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellamy？\NBellamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  瞧瞧你长多大了\NMy God, look how big you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿的什么鬼东西\NWhat the hell are you wearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,警卫制服？\Na guard's uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,靠它我才能进来这飞船\NI borrowed it to get on the drop ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人来照顾你啊\NSomeone has got to keep an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你的腕带呢？\NWhere's your wristband?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,关你啥事？\NDo you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我一年没见我哥哥了\NI haven't seen my brother in a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都没兄弟姐们啊\NNo one has a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她是Octavia Blake\NThat's Octavia Blake,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个被发现藏起来的女孩儿\Nthe girl they found hidden in the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Octavia  Octavia  不要\NOctavia, Octavia, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来做点别的\NLet's give them something else
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好让他们记住你\Nto remember you by.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？比如？\NYeah? Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,比如百年来的踏足地球第一人\NLike being the first person on the ground in 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,贱乖乖们  我们回来了！\NWe're back, bitches!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这样严肃啊  小公主？\NWhy so serious, princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是我们在大爆炸中丧命\NIt's not like we died in a fiery explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该对那倆跟随你\NTry telling that to the two guys
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,离开自己座位的人说\Nwho tried to follow you out of their seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢被叫小公主\NYou don't like being called princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  小公主？\Ndo you, princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看到那山峰了吗？\NDo you see that peak over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,韦瑟山\NMount Weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃饭就得穿过\NThere's a radiation-soaked forest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,中间那片饱经辐射的林地\Nbetween us and our next meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,丫的我们被降错地方了\NThey dropped us on the wrong damn mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那里\NThere it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经着陆了\NWe know they've landed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但通讯系统失效\Nbut communications are down,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着我们仍对地球\Nwhich means we're still blind
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一无所知\Nto conditions on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好有Abby的腕带\NThanks to Abby's wristbands,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,最起码我们还能知道\Nat least we know how those conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们身体影响变化的信息\Naffect the human body, which is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,比这百年来了解到的多得多\Nmore than we've had for 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,做的好\NSo nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  这些说明了什么？\NNow, what are they telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,两个孩子死了  已经黑屏了\NTwo dead kids, dark tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Jackson教授  请你向Kane委员解释下\NDr. Jackson, please share our theory
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的臆测\Nwith Councilor Kane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Granted  他们仅仅着陆七分钟\NGranted, they've only been on the ground for 7 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在  我们认为意外死因是\Nbut as of now, we believe the fatalities
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不安全着陆  并非辐射\Nare due to the landing, not radiation levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们与飞船失去联系时\NBoth boys died at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,两个男孩同时死去\Nthat we lost contact with the drop ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不安全着陆？这就是你们的推测？\NRough landing? That's your theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,与此相关\NThe dots connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是因为辐射  那你是否同意\NWould you agree that if it was radiation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很快就会看到死亡人数上升？\Nwe'd see fatalities climb fairly quickly now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:11:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我看显示器可是满屏红啊\NBecause I'm noticing a lot of red on that board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,生命体征数值增加  有两种可能\NSpiking vital signs, two possibilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,其一  着陆时受伤\None, injuries sustained during landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,其二呢？\NAnd the other?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿他们内心澎湃\NThey're excited to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有麻烦了\NWe got problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯系统失灵了\NThe communications system is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我去了仓顶\NI went to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大量仪表盘丢失\NA dozen panels are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,高温烧熔电线\NHeat fried the wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  现在最棘手的是\NWell, all that matters right now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,前往韦瑟山\Nis getting to Mount Weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,明白？看\NSee? Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这儿\NThis is us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们想活命\NThis is where we need to get to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿就是我们的目的地\Nif we want to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪儿学的这些？\NWhere'd you learn to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲\NYour father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  酷  地图啊\NAh, cool, a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这片镇子有酒吧吗？\NThey got a bar in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我请你啤酒\NI'll buy you a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,说话注意点儿\NYou mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿  嘿\NHey, hey, hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,拿开你的手  他是我们一伙儿的\Nhands off of him. He's with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,放松点儿\NRelax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是试图找到我们在哪儿\NWe're just trying to figure out where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在陆地上\NWe're on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这对你来说不够好吗？\NThat not good enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得找到韦瑟山\NWe need to find Mount Weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你也听到我爸说的了\NYou heard my father's message.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那才是我们该先做的\NThat has to be our first priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的老爹吧\NScrew your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么  你以为这里是你辖区吗\NWhat, you think you're in charge here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你  还有你的小公主？\Nyou and your little princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我们在意是谁管吗？\NDo you think we care who's in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要去韦瑟山\NWe need to get to Mount Weather
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不是因为长官那样说\Nnot because the Chancellor said so,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而是因为我们拖得越久\Nbut because the longer we wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就会越饥肠辘辘\Nthe hungrier we'll get
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,境况会变得更糟\Nand the harder this'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有那些补给\NHow long do you think we'll last
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你们觉得我们会撑多久？\Nwithout those supplies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去的地方有20英里的路程\NWe're looking at a 20-mile trek, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果我们想在天黑前到达\NSo if we want to get there before dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在就应动身\Nwe need to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个更好的主意\NI got a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩去  为我们找寻\NYou two go, find it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,换换特权人士来做劳苦工作吧\NLet the privileged do the hard work for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,耶  对嘛\NYeah. Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你没听到吗  我们都需要去\NYou're not listening. We all need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊  大伙儿\NLook at this, everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,地球长官啊\Nthe Chancellor of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思？\NThink that's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啊！- Wells\N- Uh! - Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对  上啊  拿下他\NYeah. Come on. Get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不  但也是  来吧\NNo, but that was. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你还能怎样啊  Wells？\NWhat you gonna do now, Wells?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊  来啊\NCome on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他只有一条腿\NKid's got one leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,何不等他好了公平决斗呢？\NHow about you wait until it's a fair fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 太空步行者\NHey, spacewalker,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,下回也救救我\Nrescue me next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？他挺可爱啊\NWhat? He's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个犯人\NHe's a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都是\NThey're all criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,听着小O  我来这里是保护你的\NLook, O. I came down here to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要保护\NI don't need protecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我被锁禁一生了\NI have been locked up one way
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一生都是如此\Nor another all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要再言听计从了\NI am done following orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我得找点乐子  Bell\NI need to have fun, Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我得放纵疯狂一下\NI need to just do something crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为我可以  现在\Njust because I can, and no one,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能阻止我  包括你\Nincluding you, is gonna stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能和他们呆一起  小O\NI can't stay with them, O.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说些什么啊？\NNow what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去找点东西吧\NGo find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我动了点手脚  好吗\NI did something, ok,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,为上飞船\Nto get on the drop ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了足以使他们一下来\Nsomething that they will kill me for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就杀了我的事儿\Nwhen they come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在还不能说是什么\NI can't say what it is just yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但你得相信我\Nbut you have to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你还相信我  是吗？\NYou do still trust me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那么韦瑟山  什么时候出发？\NSo Mount Weather. When do we leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\NRight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我们会带着食物回来\NWe'll be back tomorrow with food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你俩怎么带回\NHow are the two of you gonna carry
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,100人的口粮？\Nenough food for 100?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们四个  现在能走了吗？\N4 of us. Can we go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来不错  加我一个\NSounds like a party. Make it 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你到底在干吗？\NHey, what the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 出去走走啊  - 嘿\N- Going for a walk. - Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你试图取下这个吗？\Nwere you trying to take this off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  怎么？\NYeah. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,通过这个腕带\NSo this wristband transmits
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,方舟号会收到你的生命体征\Nyour vital signs to The Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,取下它  他们就认为你死了\NTake it off, and they'll think you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我该在乎这个吗？\NShould I care?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NWell, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只是你想爱你的人\NDo you want the people you love
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,认为你死了吗？\Nto think you're dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让他们两月后也下来吗？\NDo you want them to follow you down here in two months?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可是如果他们以为你死了\NBecause they won't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会下来了\Nif they think we're dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\NNow let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\NGo on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不该来的  Wells\NYou shouldn't have come here, Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你怎么想  Finn是我的\NBefore you get any ideas, Finn is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你怎么想  我不在乎\NBefore you get any ideas, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  亲爱的  Clarke怎么样？\NHey, darling, how's Clarke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,生命体征强健\NHer vital signs are strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,血糖偏低\Nblood sugar is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她没进食\NShe hasn't eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Griffin教授\NThis is Dr. Griffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我就来\NOn my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jackson  放下手里的活儿\NJackson, put it out there
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要输血\Nwe need blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A型阴性  大量的\N"A" Neg. And a lot of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然后马上赶往手术室\Nand then get your ass to the O.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Abby  发生什么了？\NAbby, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,长官被射伤了\NThe Chancellor has been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧  那伙计  才是老手\NNow, that, my friend, is game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西  老兄  是毒漆树\NThat, my friend, is poison sumac.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？那是？\NWhat? It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,花儿没毒\NThe flowers aren't poisonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  花可入药  用以镇定\NThey're medicinal, calming, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我家在方舟上种了很多药草\NHis family grows all the pharmaceuticals on The Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们  你们能跟上吗？\NHey, guys, would you try to keep up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  Clarke  你怎能无视这些啊\NCome on, Clarke. How do you block all this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,额  很简单啊\NWell, it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就想想为什么没见这里有动物\NI wonder, "Why haven't we seen any animals?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也许因为这儿本就没有\NMaybe it's because there are none.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也许因为我们已经暴露在\NMaybe we've already been exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,足以要了我们命的辐射里\Nto enough radiation to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿是很美  但还是跟上吧\NSure is pretty, though. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真该有人出来给她喂点儿毒漆树\NSomeone should slip her some poison sumac.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道你俩干啥被抓起来了\NI got to know what you two did to get busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,漆树不是花园里的唯一植物\NSumac is not the only herb in the garden,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你懂我的意思\Nif you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有人拿了后忘记物归原位\NSomeone forget to replace what we took.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有人道歉也有千次了吧\NSomeone has apologized, like, 1,000 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 Octavia？\NHow about you, Octavia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们抓你是因为？\NWhat'd they get you for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因为出生了\NBeing born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是老手该问的\NThat is so not game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还说没动物  啊哈？\NNo animals, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,长官失血过多\NChancellor has lost a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果及时发现他就好了  该死\NIf only they found him sooner, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他醒了\NHe's waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,再来点镇定剂\NIncrease the anesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们用了太多的血浆和镇痛剂\NWe used way too much blood and anesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,超过标准线了\NWe're way over the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的长官就要休克了\NYour Chancellor is going into shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是让我触犯法律\NYou're asking me to break the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那好  我自己来\NFine. I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们有事儿找我\NLet them come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了  先生\NExcuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,您说有消息就让来告诉您\NYou asked to be notified if there was news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,长官仍在手术中\NThe Chancellor is still in surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们已查明射杀者身份\Nbut we have I.D.Ed the shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellamy Blake  方舟上\NBellamy Blake is the only person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一一个下落不明的人\Non The Ark unaccounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁？\NWho is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不是什么人物  门警而已\NHe's no one, a janitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们仍在为其做侧写\NWe're still working up a profile,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但他去地球的动机很明确\Nbut his motive for going to Earth is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他妹妹  我记得\NSister. I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她母亲藏了她16年之久\NHer mother kept her hidden for almost 16 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,几近记录\Nnearly a record.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  Shumway指挥官  有话快说\NWhat is it, Commander Shumway. Spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在就能开始了\NWe could start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在长官手术时\NAs Chancellor pro tempore,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以下达命令\Nyou can give the order
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,执行人口缩减计划\Nto start reducing the population.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还不是时候\NNot yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我们是在浪费时间\NSir, we're wasting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,缩减百人\NRemoving the 100 from the population
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也仅仅只能换来一月光景\Nonly buys us another month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,工程师需要更多时间修理系统\NEngineering needs more than that to fix those systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果它能被修好\Nif they can fix them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白我意思  指挥官  别说了\NYou have my answer, Commander. Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们得杀害数百无辜民众\NIf we're gonna kill hundreds of innocent people,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就按照条律进行\Nwe're gonna do it by the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗？\NIs that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,与此同时  我想知道\NIn the meantime, I want to know who helped
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁帮助那个门警进入飞船\Nthis janitor get on that drop ship
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信他一人之力是无法成事的\Nbecause he sure as hell didn't do it by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来我们之中有叛徒了  指挥官\NSeems we have a traitor in our midst, Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这百人之中竟存杀手\Nand the 100 have an assassin in theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,找到水了？\NFind any water yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还没  不过…\NNo, not yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你也来的话  我再去找点\NI'm going back out if you want to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  我父亲\NYou know, my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在气压舱时\Nhe begged for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为不被放逐太空\Nin the airlock chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,而向你爸跪地求饶\Nwhen your father floated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你拼错“Die”（死）了 天才啊\NYou spelled "Die" Wrong, geniuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要杀了某人\NIf you're gonna kill someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,最好别先说出来\Nit's probably best not to announce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会是真的门警吧  是吗？\NYou're not really a member of the guard, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  不过真的马上就来\NNo. The real guard will be here soon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我们阻止他们\Nunless we stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会真的认为\NYou don't actually think
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会宽恕了你的罪名吧\Nthey're gonna forgive your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就算他们宽恕了  然后呢？\NEven if they do, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,像我们这类人\NGuys like us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还能成为模范公民吗？\Nwe're gonna become model citizens now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,找工作  幸运的话\Nget jobs, if we're lucky,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也就拾拾垃圾  - 你什么意思？\N- maybe pick up their trash? - You got a point?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么  就一个疑问\NNo. I got a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把你关起来  放逐你们到这里\NThey locked you up, dumped you down here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,像实验室里的待死白鼠\Nlike lab rats to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么还帮他们呢？\NSo why are you helping them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们傻吧\NThe hell we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还带着那些遥感呢  不是吗？\NYou're wearing those bracelets, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  这些东西正在告诉他们\NRight now, those things are telling them
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们随后下来是否安全\Nwhether or not it's safe to follow us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好  你说我们能阻止这  怎么做？\NOk. You said we could stop it. How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,先取下它\NTake them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,神舟号以为你们死了\NThe Ark will think you're dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么下来就不安全\Nthat it's not safe to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吗？\NYou follow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对  那我们取下来\NRight, and if we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我们有什么好处？\NI mean, what's in it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要有人帮我管理这里\NSomeone has got to help me run things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  Ab  长官怎么样？\NHey, Ab. How's the Chancellor doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他挺过今晚的话\NAsk me again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你再问我吧\Nif he makes it through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又失去谁了？\NWho else did we lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Murphy和Mbege家的  都叫John\NMurphy and Mbege, both named John.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在着陆时都未受伤\NNeither was injured during landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意  其他原因致死的\NI concur. Something else killed these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,上一秒  还好好的\NOne second, they were fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下一秒  就玩完儿了\Nand the next, bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不会是辐射\NThen it isn't radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托   Abby\NCome on, Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,科学可不是靠痴心妄想\NWishful thinking isn't good science.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是痴心妄想\NIt's not wishful thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,上一秒  好好的  下一秒  就死了\NOne second, fine, the next, bang
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是被辐射致死的表现\Nisn't how exposure to radiation presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  如果辐射足够强就有可能\NWell, it could be if there was enough of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果辐射足够强\NIf there was enough of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们所有人都会死\Nthey would all be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  让我对吧\NPlease let me be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  知道我一直想知道什么吗？\NHey, you know what I'd like to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么97年后送我们来这里？\NWhy send us down today after 97 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么变数吗？\NWhat changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谁管啊？我很高兴他们这样做\NWho cares? I'm just glad they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我都快在牢房发霉里\NI woke up rotting in a cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在呢  我却在树林里遛弯\Nand now I'm spinning in a forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们在卫星里发现了什么\NMaybe they found something on a satellite,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  像旧的气象卫星什么的\Nyou know, like an old weather satellite or...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是卫星\NIt wasn't a satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,方舟号资源正在枯竭\NThe Ark is dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的人口数\NAt the current population level,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也就撑个3个月\Nthere's roughly 3 months left
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,现在估计四个月吧\Nof life support,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们走了\Nmaybe 4 now that we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以为此秘密\NSo that was the secret
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们才把你关起来\Nthey locked you up to keep,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,也是为什么单独关押你\Nwhy the kept you in solitary,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲被放逐的原因？\Nfloated your old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲就是发现此缺陷的工程师\NMy father was the engineer who discovered the flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他认为人们有权利知道\NHe thought the people had a right to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而委员会反对  我妈妈也是\NThe council disagreed. My mother disagreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.57,0:22:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们担心由此会引发惊慌\NThey were afraid it would cause a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就要公诸于众  但这时  Wells…\NWe were gonna go public, anyway, when Wells...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样  告发了你父亲？\NWhat, turned in your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样  警卫在公布前早到了\NAnyway, the guard showed up before we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.06,0:22:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是今天局势造就的原因\NThat's why today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也是值得以身犯险的原因\NThat's why it was worth the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,即使我们死了  最起码\NEven if we all die, at least
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:22:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们获得了更多的时间\Nthey bought themselves more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会杀了更多人  不是吗？\NThey're gonna kill more people, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  他们这般对我\NGood. After what they did to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说  把他们都放逐了吧\NI say, float them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说真的吧\NYou don't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得去警告他们\NWe have to warn them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲也是这样说的\NThat's what my father said.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  天啊  我爱死地球了\NOh, damn, I love Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哦！ 天啊\NOh! Holy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Octavia  你到底在干吗？\NOctavia, what the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Octavia…\NOctavia...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会游泳\NI can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啊  我们可以站着啊  哈哈\NI know, but we can stand. Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  这儿不该有河流的\NWait. There's not supposed to be a river here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可是  这儿就有啊\NWell, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.71,0:23:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以赶快脱了衣服吧\NSo take off your damn clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.90,0:24:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Octavia  快上来\NOctavia, get out of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.74,0:24:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快上来啊！\NGet out of the water now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.45,0:24:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Octavia！\NOctavia!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.99,0:24:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.70,0:24:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那丫是什么东西？我们得帮她\NWhat the hell is that? We have to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.18,0:24:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们该怎么做？  - 尽量别被吃了\N- What are you gonna do? - Try not to get eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.75,0:24:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  等等\NNo. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.57,0:24:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们分散它注意力\NIf we distract it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.93,0:24:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也许它能放开她  帮我\Nit might let her go. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.98,0:24:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.18,0:24:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有用了  它放开她了\NIt worked. It let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.52,0:25:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你能上来吗？\NCan you get to the shore now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.89,0:25:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我抓到你了\NI got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.06,0:25:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,它回来了\NIt's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.62,0:25:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,它朝你去了  伙计\NIt's headed right for you, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.05,0:25:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  快啊  继续游\NCome on. Come on. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.54,0:25:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.39,0:25:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  谢谢\NThank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.67,0:25:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事了\NYou're gonna be ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.08,0:25:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我记住了\NNote to self...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.49,0:25:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如有下次  英雄救美\Nnext time, save the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.69,0:26:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,耶  继续啊  宝贝儿\NYeah. Go on, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.26,0:26:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,耶  接着啊\NYeah. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.19,0:26:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个是谁？\NWho's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.20,0:26:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在搞什么？\NWhat the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.16,0:26:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,释放自我啊\NWe're liberating ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.24,0:26:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你以为呢？\NWhat does it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.47,0:26:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你是在把我们全都害死\NIt looks like you're trying to get us all killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.08,0:26:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯系统已经毁了\NThe communication system is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.33,0:26:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就剩这些腕带了\NThese wristbands are all we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.51,0:26:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,取下它  方舟号就以为我们都死了\NTake them off, and The Ark will think we're dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.63,0:26:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会认为地球不安全\Nthat it's not safe for them to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.19,0:26:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,正是如此  长官\NThat's the point, Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.65,0:26:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能照顾好自己  对吗？\NWe can take care of ourselves, can't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.38,0:26:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,对！\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.41,0:26:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我们是来玩儿的吗？\NYou think this is a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.62,0:26:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,上边的人不仅仅有我们的亲朋好友\NThose aren't just our friends and our parents up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.14,0:26:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还有农民  医生  工程师\NThey're our farmers, our doctors, our engineers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.59,0:26:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎他给你们说了什么\NI don't care what he tells you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.64,0:26:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,依靠自己  我们无法在这儿生存\NWe won't survive here on our own...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.78,0:26:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外  如果这儿真安全\Nand besides, if it really is safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.15,0:26:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你不想让其余的人\Nhow could you not want the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.39,0:26:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也能够下来吗？\Nof our people to come down?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.64,0:26:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人都下来了\NMy people already are down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.81,0:27:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人把我的人关押起来\NThose people locked my people up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.91,0:27:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人为我母亲生了二胎\NThose people killed my mother for the crime
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.96,0:27:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而处决了她\Nof having a second child.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.63,0:27:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,都是你父亲做的\NYour father did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.21,0:27:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 法律又不是我父亲写的  - 对\N- My father didn't write the laws. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.31,0:27:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是强制执行它们\NHe enforced them,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.69,0:27:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但再也不会了\Nbut not anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.50,0:27:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿不会如此\Nnot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.41,0:27:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿  没有法律\NHere, there are no laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.88,0:27:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哇噢  耶吼  - 酷\N- Yeah. Yeah. - Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.46,0:27:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿  我们身随心动  为所欲为\NHere, we do whatever the hell we want
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.06,0:27:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为\Nwhenever the hell we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.79,0:27:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必看惯它  Wells\NNow, you don't have to like it, Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.02,0:27:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看不惯你阻止或改变它啊\NYou can even try to stop it or change it,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.88,0:27:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了我啊\Nkill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.60,0:27:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗？\NYou know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.61,0:27:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以身随心动  为所欲为\NWhatever the hell we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.42,0:27:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为！\NWhatever the hell we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.48,0:27:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为！\NWhatever the hell we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.31,0:27:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为！\Nwhatever the hell we want
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.97,0:27:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为！\Nwhatever the hell we want
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.35,0:27:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为\Nwhatever the hell we want
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.90,0:27:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为\Nwhatever the hell we want
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.78,0:27:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为\Nwhatever the hell we want
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.38,0:27:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为\Nwhatever the hell we want
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.99,0:27:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为\Nwhatever the hell we want
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.74,0:27:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为\Nwhatever the hell we want
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.77,0:27:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,身随心动  为所欲为\Nwhatever the hell we want
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.77,0:28:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨了！ 真的雨啊！\NRain! Real rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.97,0:28:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊！\NCheck it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.40,0:28:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是水！\NIt's water!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.89,0:28:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得把它收集起来\NWe need to collect this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.94,0:28:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了  身随心动  为所欲为\NWhatever the hell you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.28,0:28:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,又十个了  一个接一个的\N10 more, one after the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.89,0:28:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Abby  快看血浆渗透压\NAbby, look at plasma osmolarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.02,0:28:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,显示器表明正在上升\NIt's going up across the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.47,0:28:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们找到水源了\NThey found water.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.88,0:28:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Abigail Griffin委员\NCouncilor Abigail Griffin,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.63,0:28:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,由于你使用了\Nyou're under arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.19,0:28:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,超越医药用品的最大限量\Nfor exceeding the maximum medical supplies allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.69,0:28:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你被逮捕了\Nfor a patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.49,0:28:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  这需要公之于众\NSorry this has to be public.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.41,0:28:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,关于此事  政策规定相当明确\NThe policy in these matters is very clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.11,0:28:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没有特殊待遇\Nno special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.86,0:28:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那你到底用了多少血啊  Abby？\NHow much blood did you use, Abby?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.69,0:29:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别回答\NDon't answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.14,0:29:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,需要多少就用多少\NI used whatever it took.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.59,0:29:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,通过违法来阻止你升为长官\NBreaking the law to keep you from becoming Chancellor
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.88,0:29:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是我做过的最轻松的决定\Nwas the easiest decision I've ever made.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.22,0:29:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于此事\NIn that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.64,0:29:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你如此坦白\Ngiven your confession,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.82,0:29:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,身为临时长官\Nin my role as Chancellor pro tempore,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.16,0:29:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能定你罪行  别无他法\Nyou leave me no choice but to find you guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.16,0:29:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,办法总是人想的  Kane\NWe always have a choice, Kane.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.88,0:29:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你选择控告我的丈夫\NYou chose to press charges against my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.95,0:29:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友  即使你知道\Nyour friend, even though you knew
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.91,0:29:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他会被因此放逐\Nhe would get floated for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.17,0:29:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还将我女儿囊括在内\NYou chose to include my daughter in those charges,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.93,0:29:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你选择如此\Nand now you're choosing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.71,0:29:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,藏在法律背后  躲避一切罪责\NHiding behind the law absolves you of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.65,0:29:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就算这样  根据\NBe that as it may, in accordance
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.91,0:29:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,刑法第一条\Nwith penal code one,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.23,0:29:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,成人犯罪\Nbecause all crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.49,0:29:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,无论罪责大小\Ncommitted by those above the age of maturity
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.77,0:29:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一律死刑\Nare capital crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.10,0:29:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,由此你将被处以死刑\Nyou are hereby sentenced to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.11,0:29:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,明早行刑\NExecution is set for the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.61,0:29:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而我的选择是\Nand I choose at every turn
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.08,0:29:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不惜一切代价\Nand at any cost
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.71,0:29:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,确保\Nto make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.76,0:29:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,人类依旧存活\Nthat the human race stays alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.26,0:30:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们的不同之处  Kane\NThat's the difference between us, Kane.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.60,0:30:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我是要确保\NI choose to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.02,0:30:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是否值得活下去\Nthat we deserve to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.42,0:31:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,美呆了  对吗？\NPretty cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.09,0:31:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你去河边了？\NDid you go to the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.93,0:31:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这还是值得冒下险的\NFigured it was worth losing a finger or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.66,0:31:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.72,0:31:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你就抿一小口？\NYou call that a sip?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.94,0:32:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这会不会\NYou think this means we're all
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.29,0:32:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们都张两个脑袋？\Ngonna grow two heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.82,0:32:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呦  美女也是会笑的啊\NWhat do you know? She can laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.33,0:32:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  来看看这个\NCome on. You have to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.14,0:32:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个脚印\NThat's a toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.29,0:32:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,另外  据我判断\NPlus, near as I can tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.97,0:32:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不管它是什么  都是两只脚走路的\Nwhatever it is, it's walking on two feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.72,0:32:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜  是猴子\NMy Guess... monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.65,0:32:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啦  我只是\NI'm sorry. It's just,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.53,0:32:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知\Naccording to everything I've read,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.68,0:32:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这附近并没有两足动物的\Nthere were no bipedal animals anywhere near here,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.79,0:32:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会是猴子\Ncertainly not monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.23,0:32:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那你知不知道\NRight. You read anything about
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.56,0:32:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,森林深处有什么\Nglow-in-the-dark forests
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.19,0:32:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,或者食人蛇？\Nor man-eating snakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.68,0:33:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吧\NAre you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.73,0:33:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能随意杀害\NYou can't just kill everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.10,0:33:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,任何反对你的人\Nwho disagrees with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.34,0:33:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  你也以为我是坏人了\NNow, you all think I'm a bad guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.87,0:33:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可是只有我才能为人类存活\Nbut I'm the only one who's willing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.54,0:33:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,而愿倾尽一切\Nwhat it takes to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.12,0:33:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她可是我最好的朋友\NShe's my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.27,0:33:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那你想让我说什么\NSo what do you want me to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.24,0:33:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,说对不起？\NI'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.74,0:33:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会\NI'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.07,0:33:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,友情对我们来说奢侈难负\NFriendship is a luxury we can't afford,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.68,0:33:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就算将要变成只有亚当夏娃的宇宙\Nand if I have to take us down to a cosmic Adam and Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.89,0:33:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会如此的\NI will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.09,0:33:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  仁慈点儿吧\NPlease, show mercy,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.36,0:33:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不为Abby  为我想想吧\Nif not for Abby, then for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.96,0:33:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,仁慈也是负担\NWe can't afford mercy, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.98,0:34:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,走得够远的了\NThat's far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.02,0:34:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想射杀你  Wells\NI don't want to shoot you, Wells...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.77,0:34:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼  我倒挺喜欢你\Nhell, I like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.87,0:34:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也确实需要他们\Nbut I do need them
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.16,0:34:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,认为你死了\Nto think that you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.69,0:34:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？说真的  为什么这样做\NWhy? Why are you doing this, for real,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.82,0:34:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别说那些我说什么\Nnot some crap about getting to do
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.25,0:34:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什么的废话\Nwhat you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.01,0:34:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我有我的原因  枪也在我手里\NI have my reasons. I also have the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.91,0:34:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我来问\NSo I ask the questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.24,0:34:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我说\Nand the question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.40,0:34:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你不帮我？\Nwhy aren't you helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.84,0:34:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你老爸驱逐了你  Wells\NYou dad banished you, Wells, and yet
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.23,0:34:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,而你在这儿  仍为他做事\Nhere you are, still doing his bidding,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.48,0:34:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,遵守规则\Nfollowing the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.01,0:34:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你还没有厌烦\NAren't you tired of always doing
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.74,0:34:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一直被派遣吗？\Nwhat's expected of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.87,0:34:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,反抗他吧\NStand up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.34,0:34:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,取掉腕带  你会惊讶于\NTake off that wristband, and you'll be amazed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.62,0:34:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那种自在感觉的\Nat how good it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.54,0:34:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.07,0:34:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不  想都别想\NNever. Not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.83,0:34:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还不清楚吗？\NIs that clear enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.70,0:34:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好  知道了\NYeah. It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.37,0:35:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉得这样\NI'm sorry it had to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.25,0:35:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  放开我！不！\NNo! No! Get off of me! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.12,0:35:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,拿下他  快撂倒他\NGet him down. Put him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.38,0:35:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不！拜托  伙计  放我走\NNo! Come on, man. Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.79,0:35:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,行了  快动手\NGet it. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.56,0:35:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不！不要这样！  别这样！不  不\NNo! Don't do this! Don't do this! No. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.19,0:35:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊！\NCome on, man. Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.29,0:35:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffin教授  时间到了\NDr. Griffin, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.57,0:35:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Callie\NCallie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.47,0:36:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\NThat's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.51,0:36:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,替我照看好Clarke\NWatch out for Clarke for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.07,0:36:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.61,0:36:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jackson  好好利用腕带\NJackson, use the wristbands.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.05,0:36:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会有方法逆转设计\NThere may be a way to reverse-engineer them
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.78,0:36:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,进行通讯\Nfor communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.88,0:36:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,和Sinclair谈谈设计\NTalk to Sinclair in engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.29,0:36:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,明白就点头\NNod if you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.61,0:37:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\NStop.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.47,0:37:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffin教授被赦免了\NDr. Griffin is pardoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.41,0:37:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等会儿再处理你\NI'll deal with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.68,0:37:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,开门\NOpen the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.89,0:37:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我说  开门\NOpen the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.07,0:37:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我花了12个小时把那些内脏缝合\NI spent 12 hours putting those intestines back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.78,0:37:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在带他躺回床上\NGet him back to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.51,0:37:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,给我说说那地球百子\NTell me about the 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.52,0:37:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们成功了吗？\NDid they make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.82,0:38:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是你想打头阵的  别磨蹭了\NYou wanted to go first. Now quit stalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.33,0:38:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,韦瑟山还等着呢\NMount weather awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.93,0:38:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就荡到极点处\NJust hang on till the apogee,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.55,0:38:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你会成功的\Nand you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.46,0:38:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那会像个印第安人  是吧？\NThe apogee like the Indians, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.57,0:38:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,极点而已  又不是阿帕奇族（发音相似）\NApogee, not apache.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.20,0:38:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道的  快吧  Finn\NHe knows. Today, Finn.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.43,0:38:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  恩  队长  那边见\NAye, aye, captain. See you on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.21,0:38:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等等  - 怎么？\N- Wait. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.08,0:38:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来\NLet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.65,0:38:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以的\NI can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.19,0:38:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就知道你内心还有小宇宙\NKnew there was a badass in there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.84,0:38:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  害怕没什么的  Jasper\NHey, it's ok to be afraid, Jasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.16,0:38:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,窍门就是战胜它\NThe trick is not fighting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.33,0:38:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那边见了  啊哈！\NSee you on the other side. Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.08,0:39:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,呜 呼！耶！\NWhoo! Whoo! Whoo! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.50,0:39:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是极点！\NWe are apogee!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.27,0:39:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,耶！\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.90,0:39:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,耶！\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.37,0:39:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哈  呼！\NYes! Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.88,0:39:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好！\NYeah! Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.38,0:39:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你成功了  Jasper！\NYou did it, Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.21,0:39:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,呼哈！耶\NWhoo! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.78,0:39:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也去吧  小公主\NLet's go, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.15,0:39:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你先\NYou're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.12,0:39:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  Clarke！你也能的！\NCome on, Clarke! You got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.79,0:39:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,呜呼！  极点啊！\NWhoo! Apogee!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.84,0:40:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做到了！\NWe did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.48,0:40:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,韦瑟山！\NMount weather! Whoo! Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.95,0:40:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,帅！\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.32,0:40:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好  Jasper！\NYeah, Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.96,0:40:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jasper\NJasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.23,0:40:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  拜托  挺住  Jasper！\NCome on. Come on. Come on. Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.13,0:40:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jasper！  不  不要\NJasper! No. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.03,0:40:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下  趴下\NGet down. Get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.43,0:40:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.06,0:40:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿还有别人\NWe're not alone.
